---
import Base from '@/layouts/Base.astro';
import CTA from '@/components/CTA.astro';
import { SITE } from '@/site.config';
---

<Base
  title="Miles Sowden | Insurance Executive, Growth and Transformation"
  description="Twenty years leading Australian insurers through growth and transformation. Strategy, teams, technology, and the discipline to see it through."
  ogImage="/images/miles-sowden-headshot.jpeg"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="pt-48 pb-32 max-md:pt-32 max-md:pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-12 max-lg:px-8 max-md:px-6">
      <div class="md:flex md:items-start md:gap-16">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h1 data-reveal class="font-display text-[3.5rem] max-lg:text-5xl max-md:text-[2.5rem] leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-text-primary mb-10">
            Twenty years leading Australian insurers through growth and transformation
          </h1>
          <div data-reveal data-delay="200" class="w-[60px] h-[3px] bg-text-accent mb-8"></div>
          <p data-reveal data-delay="200" class="text-xl max-md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary mb-10">
            I lead insurers to compete better, build trust, and create lasting value. Proven across businesses with more than $1 billion in premiums, teams of 700, and five major financial institutions. Every role follows the same discipline: find root causes, design a phased strategy, then build and back the teams who execute and deliver.
          </p>
          <!-- Headshot: mobile only, between paragraph and buttons -->
          <div class="md:hidden mb-10 w-[200px]">
            <img
              src="/images/miles-sowden-headshot.jpeg"
              alt="Miles Sowden"
              width="200"
              height="150"
              class="w-full rounded-lg"
              loading="eager"
            />
          </div>
          <div data-reveal data-delay="400" class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap max-md:flex-col">
            <CTA href="#contact">
              Contact
            </CTA>
            <CTA href="#work-and-impact" variant="secondary">
              Work and impact
            </CTA>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Headshot: desktop only, right column -->
        <div class="hidden md:block w-[280px] flex-shrink-0">
          <img
            src="/images/miles-sowden-headshot.jpeg"
            alt="Miles Sowden"
            width="280"
            height="210"
            class="w-full rounded-lg"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How I lead -->
  <section class="py-32 max-md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-12 max-lg:px-8 max-md:px-6">
      <h2 data-reveal class="font-display text-[2.5rem] max-md:text-[2rem] leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.02em] text-text-primary">
        How I lead
      </h2>
      <p data-reveal class="text-xl max-md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary mt-6">
        Four patterns that hold across twenty years and five institutions. Not principles I aspire to. This is how we work together.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 max-md:grid-cols-1 gap-x-16 gap-y-12 mt-16">
        <div data-reveal class="border-t-[3px] border-text-accent pt-8">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-text-accent tracking-wide">01</span>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3 mt-2">Operate like a founder inside institutions</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Bold mandate. Refusal to accept inherited dysfunction. Then back it with cost discipline, bias to action, and personal accountability for outcomes. At CBA, this meant taking full accountability as the executive through the Royal Commission. Zero enforceable undertakings. Zero fines.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal class="border-t-[3px] border-text-accent pt-8">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-text-accent tracking-wide">02</span>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3 mt-2">Diagnose before acting</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Every role starts the same way. Map the root causes, not the symptoms. Design a strategy that sequences for impact and build capability in layers. At CBA, root cause mapping across a $1bn book preceded any structural change. Combined ratio: 101.5% to 89.2%.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal class="border-t-[3px] border-text-accent pt-8">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-text-accent tracking-wide">03</span>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3 mt-2">Organise everything around customer outcomes</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Strategy, product, technology, and measurement designed backward from what customers actually need. Not as a statement of values. As a design principle. At Westpac, this drove NPS from +25 to +44 and portfolio growth from $115m to $200m.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal class="border-t-[3px] border-text-accent pt-8">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-text-accent tracking-wide">04</span>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3 mt-2">Build teams and systems that last</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Good leadership compounds. Operating models, people development, and ways of working that grow stronger over time. At CBA, the 10-person executive team stayed in place after divestment. Staff engagement rose from 50% to 70% during the Royal Commission.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div data-reveal class="mt-12">
        <CTA href="/experience" variant="secondary" size="sm">
          Full AICD skill matrix and career history
        </CTA>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Work and impact -->
  <section class="py-32 max-md:py-20" id="work-and-impact">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-12 max-lg:px-8 max-md:px-6">
      <h2 data-reveal class="font-display text-[2.5rem] max-md:text-[2rem] leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.02em] text-text-primary">
        Work and impact
      </h2>
      <p data-reveal class="text-xl max-md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary mt-6">
        Two decades of outcomes across major Australian financial institutions, including through the Royal Commission, record catastrophe seasons, mergers and regulatory reform.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 max-md:grid-cols-1 gap-8 mt-16">
        <div data-reveal class="p-10 max-md:p-8 bg-bg-card transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-[0_16px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-2">Strata Community Insurance</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary/70 mb-4">General Manager, Data and Technology Solutions</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Built a direct insurer within a broker-dominated business. Sequenced operations, digital, then AI. Cleared a 30,000-task backlog, reduced underwriting cycle time by 19%, deployed agentic AI at 97% accuracy. Digital availability from less than 5% to 60%.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal class="p-10 max-md:p-8 bg-bg-card transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-[0_16px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-2">Commonwealth Bank</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary/70 mb-4">General Manager, General Insurance</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Led a $1 billion insurer and 700-person team through the Royal Commission, pandemic, regulatory reform, and divestment. Combined ratio from 101.5% to 89.2%. Motor profitable within 15 months, a first for the book. Digital sales from 20% to 70%. NPS from +15 to +45.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal class="p-10 max-md:p-8 bg-bg-card transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-[0_16px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-2">Hollard Insurance</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary/70 mb-4">Chief Revenue Officer</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Appointed following the CBA Insurance acquisition that doubled Hollard's business. Assessed the combined portfolio at board level, led the ASIC Pricing Promise Review across both entities, and steered entry into the Australian Government's Cyclone Reinsurance Pool for the entire group. Built enduring board relationships that continued beyond the role.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal class="p-10 max-md:p-8 bg-bg-card transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-[0_16px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-2">Westpac Banking Corporation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary/70 mb-4">Senior Management Roles</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Grew the insurance portfolio from $115m to $200m. Originated the strategic recommendation for a single alliance partner. Ran a six-month competitive process. Allianz selected. NPS from +25 to +44. Staff engagement from 66% to 92%.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal class="p-10 max-md:p-8 bg-bg-card transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-[0_16px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-2">Suncorp and Promina</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary/70 mb-4">Product Manager Roles</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Delivered the first underwriting profit in intermediated personal lines after four consecutive years of losses. Combined ratio from 105% to 98% through pricing, underwriting rules, product consolidation, claims effectiveness, and distribution rationalisation.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal class="p-10 max-md:p-8 bg-bg-card transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-[0_16px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-2">What I'm building toward</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary/70 mb-4">CEO, CXO, and NED appointments</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Compressed margins, regulatory intensity, and a technology inflection are reshaping Australian general insurance. I'm pursuing leadership roles where the mandate is to compete better through all three: allocate capital to what earns the right to grow, earn trust through how the business operates, and create lasting value by building capability that compounds.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div data-reveal class="mt-12">
        <CTA href="/experience" variant="secondary" size="sm">
          Full career detail and credentials
        </CTA>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Challenge selector -->
  <section class="py-32 max-md:py-20 bg-bg-card" id="challenges">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-12 max-lg:px-8 max-md:px-6">
      <h2 data-reveal class="font-display text-[2.5rem] max-md:text-[2rem] leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.02em] text-text-primary">
        What is your insurer facing?
      </h2>
      <p data-reveal class="text-xl max-md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary mt-6">
        Select a challenge to see relevant experience.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-12" id="archetype-buttons">
        <button data-archetype="turnaround" class="archetype-btn px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg border-[1.5px] border-border-light bg-white text-text-primary transition-all duration-200 hover:border-text-accent hover:text-text-accent cursor-pointer">
          Turnaround and combined ratio recovery
        </button>
        <button data-archetype="integration" class="archetype-btn px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg border-[1.5px] border-border-light bg-white text-text-primary transition-all duration-200 hover:border-text-accent hover:text-text-accent cursor-pointer">
          Post-merger integration
        </button>
        <button data-archetype="digital" class="archetype-btn px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg border-[1.5px] border-border-light bg-white text-text-primary transition-all duration-200 hover:border-text-accent hover:text-text-accent cursor-pointer">
          Digital and AI transformation
        </button>
        <button data-archetype="growth" class="archetype-btn px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg border-[1.5px] border-border-light bg-white text-text-primary transition-all duration-200 hover:border-text-accent hover:text-text-accent cursor-pointer">
          Growth through distribution
        </button>
        <button data-archetype="governance" class="archetype-btn px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg border-[1.5px] border-border-light bg-white text-text-primary transition-all duration-200 hover:border-text-accent hover:text-text-accent cursor-pointer">
          Board and governance capability
        </button>
      </div>
      <div id="archetype-results" class="mt-12 hidden">
        <div id="archetype-cards" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6"></div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap max-md:flex-col mt-12">
          <CTA href="#contact">
            Contact
          </CTA>
          <CTA href="#fit-finder" variant="secondary">
            Get a detailed assessment
          </CTA>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Fit Finder (simplified) -->
  <section class="py-32 max-md:py-20" id="fit-finder">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-12 max-lg:px-8 max-md:px-6">
      <h2 data-reveal class="font-display text-[2.5rem] max-md:text-[2rem] leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.02em] text-text-primary">
        Fit Finder
      </h2>
      <p data-reveal class="text-xl max-md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary mt-6">
        Paste the role requirements or key challenges. Get an executive summary of fit in under 30 seconds.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 max-w-[720px]">
        <div id="fit-input-area">
          <textarea
            id="fit-text"
            rows="6"
            placeholder="Paste the role description, key selection criteria, or the challenges the board wants addressed..."
            class="w-full p-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-text-primary bg-bg-card border-[1.5px] border-border-light rounded-lg resize-y focus:outline-none focus:border-text-accent transition-colors duration-200"
          ></textarea>
          <p id="fit-char-hint" class="text-sm text-text-secondary/70 mt-2">Minimum 100 characters</p>
          <div class="mt-6">
            <button
              id="fit-analyse-btn"
              disabled
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4.5 text-base font-medium no-underline rounded-lg transition-all duration-250 bg-bg-dark text-white border-[1.5px] border-bg-dark hover:bg-bg-dark-hover hover:border-bg-dark-hover hover:-translate-y-px disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:hover:translate-y-0 cursor-pointer"
            >
              Assess fit
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Loading state -->
        <div id="fit-loading" class="hidden">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-full bg-border-light rounded-full h-1.5 overflow-hidden">
              <div id="fit-progress-bar" class="bg-text-accent h-1.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-500" style="width: 0%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-3">Evaluating fit against 13 skill areas...</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Error state -->
        <div id="fit-error" class="hidden">
          <p id="fit-error-msg" class="text-base text-red-600 mb-4"></p>
          <button id="fit-retry-btn" class="text-sm font-medium text-text-accent hover:text-text-accent-hover cursor-pointer bg-transparent border-none">Try again</button>
        </div>
        <!-- Results -->
        <div id="fit-results" class="hidden">
          <div class="border-t-[3px] border-text-accent pt-8">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-2" id="fit-role-title"></h3>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary mb-8" id="fit-summary-text"></p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8" id="fit-top-matches"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap max-md:flex-col mt-8">
            <CTA href="#contact">
              Contact
            </CTA>
            <a href="/fit" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4.5 text-base font-medium no-underline rounded-lg transition-all duration-250 bg-transparent text-text-primary border-[1.5px] border-border-light hover:border-border-light-hover hover:bg-bg-card">
              Full analysis on the Fit Finder
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section class="py-32 max-md:py-20" id="contact">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-12 max-lg:px-8 max-md:px-6">
      <h2 data-reveal class="font-display text-[2.5rem] max-md:text-[2rem] leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.02em] text-text-primary">
        Contact
      </h2>
      <p data-reveal class="text-xl max-md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary mt-6">
        Three ways to reach me. Pick whichever suits you.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-12">
        <!-- LinkedIn -->
        <div data-reveal class="flex flex-col p-8 bg-bg-card border-t-[3px] border-text-accent">
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-text-primary mb-2">LinkedIn</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mb-6">Professional introductions and role conversations.</p>
          <div class="mt-auto">
            <CTA href={SITE.linkedIn} size="sm" external>
              Connect on LinkedIn
            </CTA>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- WhatsApp -->
        <div data-reveal class="flex flex-col p-8 bg-bg-card border-t-[3px] border-text-accent">
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-text-primary mb-2">WhatsApp</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mb-6">Direct and quick.</p>
          <div class="mt-auto">
            <CTA href={SITE.whatsApp.link('Hi Miles, I found your site and would like to connect.')} size="sm" external>
              Open WhatsApp
            </CTA>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Send a note -->
        <div data-reveal class="flex flex-col p-8 bg-bg-card border-t-[3px] border-text-accent">
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-text-primary mb-2">Send a note</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mb-4">Leave your details. I will be in touch within 24 hours.</p>
          <div class="mt-auto">
            <input
              type="text"
              id="contact-name"
              placeholder="Your name"
              class="w-full px-3 py-2 text-sm text-text-primary bg-white border-[1.5px] border-border-light rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-text-accent transition-colors duration-200 mb-2"
            />
            <input
              type="email"
              id="contact-email"
              placeholder="Your email"
              class="w-full px-3 py-2 text-sm text-text-primary bg-white border-[1.5px] border-border-light rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-text-accent transition-colors duration-200 mb-3"
            />
            <button
              id="contact-send-btn"
              disabled
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium no-underline rounded-lg transition-all duration-250 bg-bg-dark text-white border-[1.5px] border-bg-dark hover:bg-bg-dark-hover hover:border-bg-dark-hover hover:-translate-y-px disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:hover:translate-y-0 cursor-pointer"
            >
              Send
            </button>
            <p id="contact-status" class="text-xs mt-2 hidden"></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Interactive behaviour -->
  <script>
    // Challenge selector data
    const archetypes: Record<string, Array<{ company: string; role: string; metric: string; context: string }>> = {
      turnaround: [
        { company: 'Commonwealth Bank', role: 'General Manager, General Insurance', metric: 'Combined ratio: 101.5% to 89.2%', context: 'Three-year pricing programme, digital rebuild, and claims redesign across a $1bn book. Motor profitable within 15 months, a first for the portfolio.' },
        { company: 'Suncorp and Promina', role: 'Product Manager Roles', metric: 'Combined ratio: 105% to 98%', context: 'Delivered the first underwriting profit in intermediated personal lines through pricing, product consolidation, claims effectiveness, and distribution rationalisation.' },
      ],
      integration: [
        { company: 'Hollard Insurance', role: 'Chief Revenue Officer', metric: 'Portfolio governance across combined group', context: 'Assessed the combined CBA-Hollard portfolio at board level following an acquisition that doubled the business. Led regulatory sign-off across both entities.' },
        { company: 'Suncorp and Promina', role: 'Product Manager Roles', metric: 'Platform integration across $2bn GWP', context: 'Integrated products and systems across the merged Suncorp-Promina group. Rationalised broker network to profitable relationships.' },
      ],
      digital: [
        { company: 'Strata Community Insurance', role: 'GM, Data and Technology Solutions', metric: 'Digital availability: less than 5% to 60%', context: 'Sequenced operations, digital, then AI. Deployed agentic AI at 97% underwriting accuracy. Cleared a 30,000-task backlog and reduced underwriting cycle time by 19%.' },
        { company: 'Commonwealth Bank', role: 'General Manager, General Insurance', metric: 'Digital sales: 20% to 70%, headcount flat', context: 'Built channels embedded in the bank app, website, and home buying process. Quote-to-sale conversion from 20% to 50% in three months.' },
      ],
      growth: [
        { company: 'Westpac Banking Corporation', role: 'Senior Management Roles', metric: 'Portfolio growth: $115m to $200m', context: 'Originated the strategic recommendation for a single alliance partner. Ran a six-month competitive process. Allianz selected.' },
        { company: 'Commonwealth Bank', role: 'General Manager, General Insurance', metric: 'CANSTAR Outstanding Value, five consecutive years', context: 'Novel rating factor delivered 10% average premium reduction with 1% loss ratio improvement. No adverse rating on lower economic groups.' },
      ],
      governance: [
        { company: 'Commonwealth Bank', role: 'General Manager, General Insurance', metric: 'Royal Commission: zero enforceable undertakings, zero fines', context: 'Took full accountability as the executive. Quarterly entity board presentations. Reinsurance placed up to $1.9bn annually.' },
        { company: 'Hollard Insurance', role: 'Chief Revenue Officer', metric: 'ASIC Pricing Promise Review signed across both entities', context: 'Board-level portfolio assessment across the combined group. Led Cyclone Reinsurance Pool entry for the entire CBA-Hollard group.' },
      ],
    };

    // Challenge selector interaction
    document.querySelectorAll('.archetype-btn').forEach((btn) => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const key = (btn as HTMLElement).dataset.archetype;
        if (!key || !archetypes[key]) return;

        // Update button states
        document.querySelectorAll('.archetype-btn').forEach((b) => {
          b.classList.remove('border-text-accent', 'text-text-accent', 'bg-text-accent/5');
          b.classList.add('border-border-light', 'text-text-primary');
        });
        btn.classList.remove('border-border-light', 'text-text-primary');
        btn.classList.add('border-text-accent', 'text-text-accent', 'bg-text-accent/5');

        // Render matched cards
        const container = document.getElementById('archetype-cards')!;
        const cards = archetypes[key];
        container.innerHTML = cards.map((c) => `
          <div class="p-8 bg-white border-l-[3px] border-text-accent">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-text-accent mb-1">${c.company}</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-text-secondary/70 mb-3">${c.role}</p>
            <p class="text-base font-medium text-text-primary mb-2">${c.metric}</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">${c.context}</p>
          </div>
        `).join('');

        // Show results
        const results = document.getElementById('archetype-results')!;
        results.classList.remove('hidden');
      });
    });

    // Fit Finder (simplified, Phase 1 only)
    const fitText = document.getElementById('fit-text') as HTMLTextAreaElement;
    const fitBtn = document.getElementById('fit-analyse-btn') as HTMLButtonElement;
    const fitCharHint = document.getElementById('fit-char-hint')!;
    const fitInputArea = document.getElementById('fit-input-area')!;
    const fitLoading = document.getElementById('fit-loading')!;
    const fitError = document.getElementById('fit-error')!;
    const fitResults = document.getElementById('fit-results')!;
    const fitProgressBar = document.getElementById('fit-progress-bar')!;

    fitText.addEventListener('input', () => {
      const len = fitText.value.trim().length;
      fitBtn.disabled = len < 100;
      if (len === 0) {
        fitCharHint.textContent = 'Minimum 100 characters';
      } else if (len < 100) {
        fitCharHint.textContent = `${100 - len} more characters needed`;
      } else {
        fitCharHint.textContent = `${len} characters`;
      }
    });

    // Turnstile for Fit Finder
    let turnstileToken = '';
    let turnstileWidgetId: string | null = null;
    const TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY = '0x4AAAAAACpeOHmo95tCwiiA';

    function loadTurnstile() {
      if (document.querySelector('script[src*="turnstile"]')) return;
      const script = document.createElement('script');
      script.src = 'https://challenges.cloudflare.com/turnstile/v0/api.js?render=explicit';
      script.async = true;
      document.head.appendChild(script);
    }

    function renderTurnstile() {
      if (turnstileWidgetId !== null) return;
      const ts = (window as any).turnstile;
      if (!ts) return;
      const container = document.createElement('div');
      container.id = 'turnstile-widget';
      container.style.display = 'none';
      fitInputArea.appendChild(container);
      turnstileWidgetId = ts.render('#turnstile-widget', {
        sitekey: TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY,
        callback: (token: string) => { turnstileToken = token; },
        'expired-callback': () => { turnstileToken = ''; },
        'error-callback': () => { turnstileToken = ''; },
        'refresh-expired': 'auto',
        size: 'invisible',
      });
    }

    // Poll for Turnstile readiness after script loads
    function initTurnstile() {
      loadTurnstile();
      const poll = setInterval(() => {
        if ((window as any).turnstile) {
          clearInterval(poll);
          renderTurnstile();
        }
      }, 200);
      // Stop polling after 30s
      setTimeout(() => clearInterval(poll), 30000);
    }

    // Load Turnstile early, also on focus as fallback
    setTimeout(initTurnstile, 2000);
    fitText.addEventListener('focus', initTurnstile, { once: true });

    async function analyseFit() {
      const text = fitText.value.trim();
      if (text.length < 100) return;

      fitInputArea.classList.add('hidden');
      fitError.classList.add('hidden');
      fitResults.classList.add('hidden');
      fitLoading.classList.remove('hidden');

      // Animate progress bar
      let progress = 0;
      const progressInterval = setInterval(() => {
        progress = Math.min(progress + Math.random() * 8, 90);
        fitProgressBar.style.width = `${progress}%`;
      }, 300);

      // Wait for Turnstile token (max 10s)
      const tokenStart = Date.now();
      while (!turnstileToken && Date.now() - tokenStart < 10000) {
        await new Promise((r) => setTimeout(r, 200));
      }

      if (!turnstileToken) {
        clearInterval(progressInterval);
        fitLoading.classList.add('hidden');
        fitError.classList.remove('hidden');
        document.getElementById('fit-error-msg')!.textContent =
          'Security verification timed out. Please refresh the page and try again.';
        return;
      }

      try {
        const controller = new AbortController();
        const timeout = setTimeout(() => controller.abort(), 60000);

        const res = await fetch('/api/fit', {
          method: 'POST',
          headers: {
            'Content-Type': 'application/json',
            'X-Turnstile-Token': turnstileToken,
          },
          body: JSON.stringify({ text }),
          signal: controller.signal,
        });
        clearTimeout(timeout);

        if (!res.ok) {
          const err = await res.json().catch(() => ({ error: 'Analysis failed' }));
          throw new Error(err.error || `Error ${res.status}`);
        }

        const data = await res.json();

        clearInterval(progressInterval);
        fitProgressBar.style.width = '100%';
        await new Promise((r) => setTimeout(r, 300));

        // Render results
        const titleEl = document.getElementById('fit-role-title')!;
        const summaryEl = document.getElementById('fit-summary-text')!;
        const matchesEl = document.getElementById('fit-top-matches')!;

        titleEl.textContent = data.roleTitle || 'Role fit assessment';
        summaryEl.textContent = data.summary;

        const topMatches = data.topMatches || {};
        matchesEl.innerHTML = Object.entries(topMatches).map(([key, match]: [string, any]) => `
          <div class="p-6 bg-bg-card border-l-[3px] border-text-accent">
            <p class="text-xs font-medium text-text-accent uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">${key === 'skillset' ? 'Strongest skill match' : 'Strongest mindset match'}</p>
            <p class="text-base font-medium text-text-primary mb-2">${match.headline || match.skillArea || ''}</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">${match.matchReason || ''}</p>
          </div>
        `).join('');

        fitLoading.classList.add('hidden');
        fitResults.classList.remove('hidden');

      } catch (e: any) {
        clearInterval(progressInterval);
        fitLoading.classList.add('hidden');
        fitError.classList.remove('hidden');
        document.getElementById('fit-error-msg')!.textContent = e.message || 'Something went wrong. Please try again.';
      }

      // Reset Turnstile for next attempt
      turnstileToken = '';
      if (turnstileWidgetId && (window as any).turnstile) {
        (window as any).turnstile.reset(turnstileWidgetId);
      }
    }

    fitBtn.addEventListener('click', analyseFit);

    document.getElementById('fit-retry-btn')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      fitError.classList.add('hidden');
      fitInputArea.classList.remove('hidden');
    });

    // Contact form: send a note
    const contactName = document.getElementById('contact-name') as HTMLInputElement;
    const contactEmail = document.getElementById('contact-email') as HTMLInputElement;
    const contactSendBtn = document.getElementById('contact-send-btn') as HTMLButtonElement;
    const contactStatus = document.getElementById('contact-status')!;

    function validateContact() {
      const name = contactName.value.trim();
      const email = contactEmail.value.trim();
      contactSendBtn.disabled = !(name.length > 0 && /^[^\s@]+@[^\s@]+\.[^\s@]+$/.test(email));
    }

    contactName.addEventListener('input', validateContact);
    contactEmail.addEventListener('input', validateContact);

    contactSendBtn.addEventListener('click', async () => {
      const name = contactName.value.trim();
      const email = contactEmail.value.trim();
      if (!name || !email) return;

      contactSendBtn.disabled = true;
      contactSendBtn.textContent = 'Sending...';

      try {
        const res = await fetch('/api/contact', {
          method: 'POST',
          headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
          body: JSON.stringify({ name, email }),
        });

        if (!res.ok) throw new Error('Failed to send');

        contactStatus.textContent = 'Sent. I will be in touch within 24 hours.';
        contactStatus.className = 'text-xs mt-2 text-text-accent';
        contactStatus.classList.remove('hidden');
        contactSendBtn.textContent = 'Sent';
        contactName.disabled = true;
        contactEmail.disabled = true;
      } catch {
        contactStatus.textContent = 'Could not send. Please try LinkedIn or WhatsApp instead.';
        contactStatus.className = 'text-xs mt-2 text-red-600';
        contactStatus.classList.remove('hidden');
        contactSendBtn.textContent = 'Send';
        contactSendBtn.disabled = false;
      }
    });
  </script>

